import Cabecalho from "./Cabecalho";
import { Button, Form, Label, Col, Input, FormGroup } from "reactstrap";
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css";

const Cadastro = () => {
  return (
    <main>
      <Cabecalho />
      <Form>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="Email" sm={2}>
            Email
          </Label>
          <Col sm={5}>
            <Input
              id="Email"
              name="email"
              placeholder="digite seu email"
              type="email"
            />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="senha" sm={2}>
            Senha
          </Label>
          <Col sm={5}>
            <Input
              id="examplePassword"
              name="password"
              placeholder="digite sua senha"
              type="password"
            />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="exampleDate">Date</Label>
          <Col sm={5}>
            <Input
              id="exampleDate"
              name="date"
              placeholder="date placeholder"
              type="date"
            />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <legend className="col-form-label col-sm-2">Qual seu gÃªnero?</legend>
        <Col sm={5}>
          <FormGroup check>
            <Input name="radio2" type="radio" /> <Label check>Masculino</Label>
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup check>
            <Input name="radio2" type="radio" /> <Label check>Feminino</Label>
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup check>
            <Input name="radio2" type="radio" /> <Label check>Outro</Label>
          </FormGroup>
        </Col>
      </Form>
    </main>
  );
};

export default Cadastro;
